{"tid":530931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全球自由度報告】香港續跌僅得59分 政治權利與伊拉克同分","createTime":"2018-01-16T09:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T09:39:11.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1effb155ebf432e05a07abce276e200952d66a31","tid":530931,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180116/large/1516093879_79d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180116%2Flarge%2F1516093879_79d0.jpg&h=75c92008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180116/large/1516093906_9297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180116%2Flarge%2F1516093906_9297.jpg&h=adc1fbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國人權機構自由之家（Freedom House）發表全球自由度報告，香港的自由度總分得59分(0分為最不自由、100分為最自由)，屬partly free(局部自由)的地區，總分較去年及前年的61及63分低，而在各項分數中(1分為最好，7分最差)，公民權利得2分；新聞自由狀況屬partly free(局部自由)，政治權利只有5分，與被評為不自由地區的伊拉完分數一樣。<br />\n<br />\n該組織認為，本港的總分下降主要因為部分社運人士被判入獄、4名立法會議員被褫奪議員資格，以致令立法會議事規則被修改，以及早前全國人大常委會通過將《國歌法》納入香港《基本法》附件三等事件，又認為中共逐漸增加對香港管治的影響，去打壓提倡民主自決等運動亦影響了香港的自由度。<br />\n<br />\n至於鄰近國家或地區方面，中國總分為14分，被定為不自由，台灣總分為93分、南韓為84分、日本為96分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180116/57715006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57715006&d=5lQWy1R1WVXVkzQq1%2B40NS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bf961623\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F57715006&h=79a4a999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180116/57715006</a>"},{"pid":"2e5644774fe35555a2071a13a94f64f4ab476c3e","tid":530931,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://freedomhouse.org/report/freedom-world/freedom-world-2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhouse.org%2Freport%2Ffreedom-world%2Ffreedom-world-2018&d=5lQWy1R1WVXVkzQq1%2B40NS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fc9f41a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://freedomhouse.org/report/freedom-world/freedom-world-2018</a><br />\n<br />\n補返條link"},{"pid":"88a4ec2a854e1c0e71ee53bd2dbb3339bd65d9fd","tid":530931,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1440073eec234d22b9f504635943007b5bf6f040","tid":530931,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30553b992c3926ba50a2cabfb9551b804f87cc1c","tid":530931,"uid":88855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申bc"},{"pid":"c4475364e25487ca98f155064cae6c8ba88c5bda","tid":530931,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e329034a9584698af886dcd7e38087e6a52e5c1e","tid":530931,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"俾想像中高"}]}